introduction: Whether trekking through the remote jungles of Cambodia in search of a legendary ape-man or exploring the secrets of the world’s largest cave system right here in the United States, the EXPEDITION X team is taking viewers to the stranger side of the unknown.S4 E1 - Terror in Appalachia（阿帕拉契恐怖山怪）S4 E2 - The Van Meter Monster（凡米特怪物）S4 E3 - Thailand's UFO CultS4 E4 - Graveyard of the Great Lakes（大湖区坟场）S4 E5 - Ghost Fort of the Civil War（幽灵堡垒）S4 E6 - Civil War Ghosts in the Bay（海湾内战幽魂）
